SUMMARY:Castalia
DESCRIPTION:Hugo House welcomes back Castalia—University of Washington MFA program's monthly reading series featuring graduate students\, faculty\, and alumni. Showcasing published and unpublished drafts of work by authors from a variety of disciplines\, professional backgrounds\, and age demographics\, Castalia offers authors a platform for community reading while putting their work in conversation with other voices\, styles\, concerns\, and identities.
URL:https://hugohouse.org/event/castalia_2026-04-15/
END:VEVENT
